[How To Use Git and Github (Long) Tutorial](https://www.udacity.com/course/how-to-use-git-and-github--ud775)<br></li>

<li>Join the Slack Channel <br>
I found out too late that there‚Äôs a #CLI-data-gem-project channel. There is lots of good info, very helpful people, and it sure is nice to know other people feel your pain!</li>

